	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia Christi tecum.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Hospinianus</persName> noster sit loco epistolę, mi Bullingere, frater in Christo pie et observande.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Is procul dubio bona fide omnes res nostras apud te deponet.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego si plura scribere conarer, non possum tamen, cum iam octiduo fere graviter laborarim erysypila ita, ut ex grabbatulo nonnisi pedo innixus promoveam etc.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eum morbum, si propitio numini visum fuerit, mihi aliquando fatalem existimo; adeo graviter et importune ac saepius me molestat.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fiat domini voluntas.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ut pergant vicini nostri <placeName type="auto_name">Keiserspergani</placeName> cum <placeName type="auto_name">Monasterianis</placeName> in valle <persName type="auto_name">S. Gregorii</persName> significabit <persName type="auto_name">Hospinianus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Baro <placeName type="auto_name">Rapoltsteinensis</placeName> agit cum principi <placeName type="auto_name">Montbelgardi</placeName> consilium quęrens, quo <placeName type="auto_name">Ensenheimensibus</placeName> adversariis respondeat etc.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in Christo Iesu.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora pro me deum per Iesum Christum, amen.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta fratres omnes nominatim.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l411" cert="high">Richenvillę</placeName> 4. iunii 1556.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus tuissimus <persName ref="p1010" cert="high">Erbius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Lieber her Bullinger, helffent dem <persName ref="p7073" cert="high">Hospiniano</persName> etwa umb 10 agenden, damit wirs den <foreign xml:lang="la">renascentibus ecclesiis</foreign> khunden mitteilen und <foreign xml:lang="la">in administratione sacramentorum concordes seyent etc.</foreign></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viro pręstantissimo pietate inprimis ac doctrina d. Henrycho Bullingero, ecclesię Tigurinę antistiti, fratri observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
